<c74object name='sp.slicecurve' category='' module='SP-Tools'>
    <digest>Divides a normalized space into equal or irregularly-spaced slices
</digest>
    <description>Divides a normalized space into equal or irregularly-spaced slices.
</description>
    <discussion><h4><openfilelink filename="SP-Tools Overview.maxpat">Open the Overview Patch</openfilelink></h4>
The <o>sp.slicecurve</o> object takes incoming numbers (either as jump indices or MIDI note numbers) and converts these into slices of a normalized space. These can be evenly spaced or with a curve applied to create irregularly-spaced slices.ch using a single float from a controller or UI object.
</discussion>

